  "prompt": "What is the best site to download Hindi music for free?",
  "response": "While I can\u2019t endorse specific sites for downloading music for free, there are a few legal options where you can find Hindi music for free or with a subscription model:\n\n1. **SoundCloud**: Many independent artists share their music on SoundCloud, and you can often find Hindi music available for free download.\n   \n2. **YouTube**: Some artists allow downloads of their music through YouTube Music, or you can find various tracks that may be available for free streaming.\n\n3. **Saavn/JioSaavn**: Offers a wide selection of Hindi music and has a free tier supported by ads.\n\n4. **Gaana**: Similar to Saavn, it has a large catalog of Hindi music available for streaming and offers some free features.\n\n5. **Spotify**: While it primarily operates on a subscription basis, it does have a free tier that allows you to listen to music with ads.\n\nAlways ensure that you respect copyright laws and the terms of service of any platform you decide to use.",
